Reasoning: The paper deals with measuring the meaning of words in a conceptual environment, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of the World-Wide Web as a source of data also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the analysis of the meaning bounds for different words could also be relevant to the study of complex systems (cs.CY).
